name: SCRAMBLER | WHITE 26''
description: The THRILLS SCRAMBLER is a hybrid 2 wheeled street machine blast from the past. A classic mix of a BMX racer but with the larger 26' Sunday cruiser frame. The THRILLS SCRAMBLER features the unique and original triangle frame.  The SCRAMBLER also combines tracking or a free spinning option with just a simple rotation of the back wheel

name: BUSH RANGER | BROWN
description: THRILLS has collaborated with Australian hat legend Bill Connors from BC Hats Byron Bay to create the BUSH RANGER hat. The BUSH RANGER hat is made with a high grade and extremely durable leather. The brim is reinforced with a high tensile fencing wire allowing it to be shaped to your style. The BUSH RANGER Leather hat has been treated with waxes and oils to guard against the elements. Handmade in Byron Bay
